reviewText: The presentation was well done and the information was pitched perfectly with clear actions for the viewer to work through.
This was OK, but it is really only a once through listen to.  Or maybe a twice through. I recommend people check it out at their library.
I LOVE TO GET INFORMED ON ALL KINDS OF HEALTH ISSUES. EVERYONE SHOULD HAVE THESE DVD'S ON HAND.  I HAVE STARTED MY OWN HEALTH LIBRARY!  THANKS TO THE MAYO CLINIC WELLNESS SOLUTIONS.
